{"data":[{"name":"81:1","price":"Idan rãna aka shafe haskenta","arabic":"إِذَا ٱلشَّمۡسُ كُوِّرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5801,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"81:2","price":"Kuma idan taurãri suka gurɓãce (wani ya shiga a cikin wani).","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلنُّجُومُ ٱنكَدَرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5802,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"81:3","price":"Kuma idan duwãtsu aka tafiyar da su.","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡجِبَالُ سُيِّرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5803,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"81:4","price":"Kuma idan rãƙuma mãsu cikunna* aka sakẽ su wãwai, bã ga kõwa ba.","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡعِشَارُ عُطِّلَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5804,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"* Rãƙuma mãsu ciki ɗan wata gõma.","lang":"ha"},{"name":"81:5","price":"Kuma idan dabbõbin dãji aka tattara su.","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡوُحُوشُ حُشِرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5805,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"81:6","price":"Kuma idan tẽkuna aka mayar da su wuta.","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡبِحَارُ سُجِّرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5806,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"81:7","price":"Kuma idan rãyuka aka haɗa* su da jikunkunansu.","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلنُّفُوسُ زُوِّجَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5807,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"* Ko kuma, aka haɗa kõwane mutum da irin mutãnensa a Aljanna ko a wuta.","lang":"ha"},{"name":"81:8","price":"Kuma idan wadda aka turbuɗe* ta da rai aka tambaye ta.","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡمَوۡءُۥدَةُ سُئِلَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5808,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"* A cikin zãmanin jahiliyya Lãrabãwa bã su son a haifa musu 'ya'ya mãta dõmin haka har sukan turbuɗe 'ya'yansu dõmin kada su yi abin kunya ko kuma su talauce wajen yi musu aure.","lang":"ha"},{"name":"81:9","price":"\"Sabõda wane laifi ne aka kashe ta?\"","arabic":"بِأَيِّ ذَنۢبٖ قُتِلَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5809,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"81:10","price":"Idan takardun ayyuka aka wãtsa su (ga mãsu su).","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلصُّحُفُ نُشِرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5810,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"81:11","price":"Kuma idan sama aka fẽɗe ta.","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلسَّمَآءُ كُشِطَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5811,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"81:12","price":"Kuma idan Jahĩm aka hũra ta","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡجَحِيمُ سُعِّرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5812,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"81:13","price":"Kuma idan Aljanna aka kusantar da ita.","arabic":"وَإِذَا ٱلۡجَنَّةُ أُزۡلِفَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5813,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"81:14","price":"Rai ya san abin da ya halartar (a rãnar nan).","arabic":"عَلِمَتۡ نَفۡسٞ مَّآ أَحۡضَرَتۡ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5814,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"81:15","price":"To, ba sai Na yi rantsuwa da taurãri matafã* ba.","arabic":"فَلَآ أُقۡسِمُ بِٱلۡخُنَّسِ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5815,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"* Masu tafiya suna kõmawa bãya.","lang":"ha"},{"name":"81:16","price":"Mãsu gudu suna ɓũya.","arabic":"ٱلۡجَوَارِ ٱلۡكُنَّسِ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5816,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"81:17","price":"Da dare idan ya bãyar da bãya.","arabic":"وَٱلَّيۡلِ إِذَا عَسۡعَسَ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5817,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"81:18","price":"Da sãfiya idan ta yi lumfashi.","arabic":"وَٱلصُّبۡحِ إِذَا تَنَفَّسَ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5818,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"81:19","price":"Lalle ne shi (Alƙur'ãni) haƙƙan, maganar wani manzon (Allah) ne mai girma ga Allah.","arabic":"إِنَّهُۥ لَقَوۡلُ رَسُولٖ كَرِيمٖ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5819,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"81:20","price":"Mai ƙarfi, mai daraja a wurin Mai Al'arshi.","arabic":"ذِي قُوَّةٍ عِندَ ذِي ٱلۡعَرۡشِ مَكِينٖ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5820,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"81:21","price":"Wanda ake yi wa ɗã'a (wato shugaban malã'iku) ne a can, amintacce.","arabic":"مُّطَاعٖ ثَمَّ أَمِينٖ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5821,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"81:22","price":"Kuma abokinku ba mahaukaci ba ne.","arabic":"وَمَا صَاحِبُكُم بِمَجۡنُونٖ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5822,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"81:23","price":"Kuma lalle ne, yã gan shi* a cikin sararin sama mabayyani.","arabic":"وَلَقَدۡ رَءَاهُ بِٱلۡأُفُقِ ٱلۡمُبِينِ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5823,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"* Annabi ya ga Mala'ika Jibirilu ya san shi. Sabõda haka wani aljani bã zai yi kama da shi ba balle ya kãwo masa ƙarya.","lang":"ha"},{"name":"81:24","price":"Kuma shi, ga gaibi* bã mai rowa ba ne.","arabic":"وَمَا هُوَ عَلَى ٱلۡغَيۡبِ بِضَنِينٖ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5824,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"* Ma'anar gaibi a nan, ilmin da Allah Ya aiko Jibirilu da shi zuwa ga Annabi Annabi ba ya ɓõye shi daga mutãne. Ga wata ƙira'a, wanda ake tuhuma, wãto ba a tuhumar Annabi, ga gaibin da ya faɗi cewa daga Allah yake, wato Alƙur'ãni duka gaskiya ne.","lang":"ha"},{"name":"81:25","price":"Kuma shi (Alƙur'ani) bã maganar shaiɗani, wanda aka la'ana, ba ce.","arabic":"وَمَا هُوَ بِقَوۡلِ شَيۡطَٰنٖ رَّجِيمٖ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5825,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"81:26","price":"Shin, a inã zã ku tafi?","arabic":"فَأَيۡنَ تَذۡهَبُونَ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5826,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"81:27","price":"Lalle ne shi (Alƙur'ãni), bã kõme ba ne fãce gargaɗi ga talikai.","arabic":"إِنۡ هُوَ إِلَّا ذِكۡرٞ لِّلۡعَٰلَمِينَ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5827,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"81:28","price":"Ga wanda ya so, daga cikinku, ya shiryu.","arabic":"لِمَن شَآءَ مِنكُمۡ أَن يَسۡتَقِيمَ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5828,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"},{"name":"81:29","price":"Kuma bã zã ku so ba sai idan Allah Ubangijin halitta Yã yarda.","arabic":"وَمَا تَشَآءُونَ إِلَّآ أَن يَشَآءَ ٱللَّهُ رَبُّ ٱلۡعَٰلَمِينَ","category":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir"],"ayahNumber":5829,"juzNumber":30,"footnotes":"","lang":"ha"}],"chapter":["81 (At-Takwir)","At-Takwir","Surah At-Takwir","Chapter At-Takwir","Takwir","Surah Takwir","Chapter Takwir","At Takwir","Surah At Takwir","Chapter At Takwir","Surah 81","Chapter 81","The Overthrowing","التكوير"]}